body_html:
If you didn't check out 1.2 you will get master, not 1.2, which contains strictly more stuff.

What compiler are you using to build this? Because this compilation error happens while compiling a CUDA file, maybe there's a problem with the nvcc version you're using (assuming you're using nvcc).
